text: Finca Barú del Pacífico Mixed Wildlife Refuge (), is a protected area in Costa Rica, managed under the Central Pacific Conservation Area, it was created in 1995 by decree 24639-MIRENEM. == References == Category:Costa Rica Category:Protected areas Category:Nature reserves in Costa Rica Category:Protected areas established in 1995
title: Finca Barú del Pacífico Mixed Wildlife Refuge
